gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Knicks 111, Nets 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Knicks defeated the Nets, 111-107. Jalen Brunson led the Knicks (30 points, 11 assists, zero turnovers) as Josh Hart added 16 points and seven rebounds. Cam Thomas led the Nets with 41 points and six assists in the loss. The Knicks have now won four in a row to improve to 49-32 while the Nets move to 32-49.
